data.description: One Floor Living at its BEST!!   Take a look at your new home!  This adorable rancher boasts an open floor plan on a park like setting spacious lot.  Home has 3 bedrooms, full bath and the master suite has half bath and walk in closet.  Freshly painted, Updated bathrooms, laminate flooring, newer appliances and windows.  Has fenced in rear yard with a large covered porch/deck and storage shed.  New dimensional roof installed in 2014, paved driveway, house just pressure washed, and landscaped.  Great Neighborhood!! Home is Convenient to all major Interestates and shopping but has private suburban living .   This is the perfect starter home & a must see!!
